parameters: There is one crystal placed in each map.
You can recover here, so please make use of it for dungeon conquest.
Are you ready in your heart?
あ、いえ、まだちょっと・・・
Three monsters are blocking the path ahead.
I've been looking forward to this day for so long!
Listen up, all of you! My name is Okuni-sama!

Bow down and obediently hand over the women to me, the one who will
soon conquer the world!

What nonsense are you talking about? There's no way we're going to
lose.
I see... You do give off a dangerous vibe, but...
Ugh! I'll do whatever it takes!
Damn it! I'm sorry, both of you!
I did it! I succeeded! I was able to reproduce the power of the demon!
If that dangerous guy wasn't here, everything would be ours!
Alright! Both of you, let's do this!
\n[1], let's do it! The two of us together can definitely win!
Damn it! This kid is strong too!

Okunii... This is our true strength. Let's live within our means from
now on.
Damn it! I won't give up! Remember that!

Phew... As expected, both of you. So, are you still planning to keep
going?

No, I don't have any intention of fighting against opponents I can't
beat.

From now on, I'll take responsibility and keep an eye on you. I won't
let you interfere.
If it's you guys, maybe you can even save that girl... Farewell!
Shaa! This is just a rough estimate!
Then, as I declared, I'll be taking this girl!
What should I do... at this rate... I...
Huh? What's wrong, Okusuke? Sorry, but this girl is my prey.
That girl doesn't belong to anyone, of course not to you, Okunii.

...You've always been a pain, and we've never seen eye to eye. But
this time, I'm really getting fed up with you, you know?
That's my line. I don't think I can overlook you anymore!

Don't worry about it. I did it on my own. You guys will continue on
ahead, right?
Let me... take care of you!
In the end, I was saved, so I can't just leave you alone like that!
I'll be by your side taking responsibility until you recover!
When Lira gets like this, she's stubborn, so you can do as you like.
If it's something Lira has decided, there's nothing more to say.
Well then, that's how it is, so take care of me, Okusuke-san!
"1_t=11_subject=最近の想像相手　おくすけ"

Due to fatigue from the battle, we decided to return to the village
for now.
Hehe... Well then, when we get back, I'll pamper you plenty.
"1_t=11_subject=最近の想像相手　おくにぃ"
Are you ready in your heart?
Are you ready in your heart?
あ、いえ、まだちょっと・・・
Indeed, it's a creepy monster, isn't it?
But there's no other way but to move forward here.
That's right, let's put our spirits into it and move forward...!

Shit! There's a swarm of them... I'll take care of these two, \n[1],
cooperate with Miiru and take care of the one in front!
Hurry and take them down, then support Light!
It seems Light has already taken care of his side.

It seems like we need to be even more cautious in our future
exploration if there are monsters like this around.

I'm sorry for surprising you. My name is Ray... I am the prince of the
fairy kingdom.
I knew it... Ray! You're alive!? But, what about the fairy kingdom...

Indeed, our country was destroyed by monsters... However, I have
gathered surviving comrades and am creating a new fairy kingdom.

I have been working tirelessly to stabilize the foundation of the
kingdom, and I apologize for taking so long to come and pick up
Princess Miiru.

However, Princess Miiru, we have been able to reunite fatefully like
this... Would you please become my partner, just as your distant
parents wished for...
That's... but... even if you suddenly say something like that, I...
\n[1]... Yes, I understand. I will go with Ray.
It is my duty to fulfill the wishes of my father and mother.

Princess... Thank you. Well then, let us promptly head to our country.
I will guide you.

After that, due to fatigue from the battle, we decided to return to
the village for the time being.
Y-You don't have to say it like that...
Princess...! We need to hurry and follow! Excuse me--
There might have been a better way to say that.

Such a princess! Just how much has the prince done for you until
now...?!
...Phew, I never expected that tomboy Miiru to change this much.
You weren't that much of a tomboy, were you?
Haha... I hope you find happiness.
Yeah... Ray, do your best too.
Well, it's time to withdraw. I hope you all have a happy future.
Are you relieved? He is your...
I feel a little guilty, but if it's Ray, I'm sure it'll be okay.
I want to stay here... Is that not allowed?

It's something Miiru decided, so there's no need for anyone to
interfere.
\n[1] really isn't obedient at all, huh?

We were also tired from the battle, so we decided to return to the
village for now.
Are you ready in your heart?
Are you ready in your heart?
あ、いえ、まだちょっと・・・
There is a horde of monsters ahead.
There are monsters here. Let's kick their butts.
There are a lot of them, so be careful.

There are monsters coming from behind...! I'll take care of them, so
I'll leave the ones in front to \n[1] and the others!
If we handle this calmly, we'll be okay.
Let's keep going at this pace, steadily getting stronger.

Damn... It's a bit troublesome when there are so many of them, after
all.

It's okay... Let's coordinate as a team of three and deal with them
properly.

In this map, special battle events will occur for each heroine
accompanying you.

Depending on the outcome of the event, the heroine may have a tough
time, so please be careful.
